  "description": {
    "zh": "你好啊，雇佣兵。又来看望老年人了？坐下吧，想喝点茶吗？不要？随你吧。听好了，一群拾荒者又出现在了那个地方。我们需要给这些人一点颜色看看，这样以后再来的人也会被吓到了。所以我在想，为什么不让你去拿着斧头大砍一通呢？你能做到吧？我就不信了，看哪个混蛋还敢再去淌这一条血路。",
    "en": "Well, hello there, mercenary. Come to see the old man? Sit down, would you like some tea? No? All right, then. Listen, a gang of looters showed up in the area again. We've got to get them away from this place for good, so that even those who come after them would have a heart attack. So I'm thinking, why don't you take an axe and chop them the fuck up, eh? Can you do that? I don't think any bastard's gonna dare get into that bloodbath afterwards."
  },
